    "en": {
      "title": "Price Control for Eggs: Special Gazette Issue",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Consumer Affairs Authority has issued a special gazette notification fixing the maximum retail price for eggs with effect from midnight yesterday (19).",
        "Accordingly, the maximum retail price of a white egg has been fixed at Rs 43 and the maximum retail price of a red egg has been fixed at Rs 45.",
        "The Consumer Affairs Authority said that traders who sell eggs at prices higher than this fixed price will be fined. (a)"
      ],
